data.description: Welcome to this beautiful home located in the Forest Glen at Kelly Farms subdivision. This well maintained one owner property has so many great things to offer, with a main floor primary suite including heated tile flooring in the ensuite, recently refinished hardwood floors, newer carpet, beautiful landscaping, a partially finished basement and loads of storage. Two spacious bedrooms, bathroom, and a large loft grace the second floor. An additional bedroom, bathroom, theatre room, bar, pool table area and two large storage rooms finish out the interior in the garden level basement. There is the possibility of adding two additional bedrooms if needed, one in the basement, and one on the second floor. The exterior doesn't disappoint with beautiful mature landscaping, established bird houses, many perennial flowers/bushes, and backing to a 40' greenbelt which adds privacy and serenity in the backyard. Under the deck you will find a screened in porch area that is great for relaxing bug-free evening. Come see your new home today!
